rComments: His class examples are very good, however, he is a very unorganized professor when it comes to informing the class of administrative information. Every section had their assignment given at least two weeks in advance, and he sent it out one week in advance and did not really change the due date. He also has very specific and hard grading criteria.

Excellent professor! He talks really slow in lectures, giving you enough time to react at a timely pace with him. He provided a lot of good examples to make you understand abstract concepts. He is also willing to spend time after lectures to answer your questions. Participation is not part of your marking, but don't skip lectures if you want A.
Best prof I have had so far!  Very clear, gave lots of good examples.  If your going to take this course, register in his section if you can!
Best prof I have had so far!  Explanations were clear, and examples were very helpful. Very approachable.

professor shear is a good guy. his lectures actually let help you understand the law which can be confusing, if you don't like school you don't have to come to lecture he gives everyone handwritten notes of the whole course. his tests and assignments are pretty fair and he answers every single question in class what more can you ask for?
